Class Solver

  • java.lang.Object
    • pkg2048_plus_4096.Solver

  • public class Solver
extends java.lang.Object
    The class is used to implement the Solver mode of the game 2048+4096. It consists of all the methods used to implement the Solver. The solver is based on the the AlphaBeta Pruning Algorithm.
